original_title: Horror in Idaho: The Student Murders
overview: What happened when terror gripped the rural town of Moscow, Idaho, when authorities found four University of Idaho students ― Ethan Chapin (20), Madison Mogen (21), Xana Kernodle (20) and Kaylee Goncalves (21) ― stabbed to death in an off-campus house in November.
title: Horror in Idaho: The Student Murders
